<recipe lang="en-uk">
    <title><![CDATA[Risotto Indivia, Nocciole, e Scamorza]]></title>
    <description><![CDATA[A recipe from a Vercelli rice grower, done with brown risotto rice]]></description>
    <source><![CDATA[http://www.speckandthecity.com/2012/01/risotto-integrale-con-invidia-belga.html]]></source>
